Package: vibble
Title: Tidy-Data Utilies for Medical Imaging Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Jan", "Kueckelhaus", , "jan.kueckelhaus@uk-erlangen.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4211-4386"))
Description: A tidy-data framework for voxel-based medical imaging. Defines the “vibble”, a tibble representation of voxel data in shared spatial spaces, with tools for reading, transforming, annotating, and visualising 3D volumes. Includes utilities for 2D slicing, spatial metadata handling, and a ggplot2-compatible plotting grammar for masks, labels, and numeric overlays.
